Usage: recreatePtnCellBlockage [-help] [<ptnName>] [-noPinCutSpace  | -hasPinCutSpace ] [-noViaCutSpace  | -hasViaCutSpace ]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
<ptnName>          # Specifies name of the partition, wildcard can be specified
                   # (string, optional)
-hasPinCutSpace    #   (bool, optional)
-hasViaCutSpace    #   (bool, optional)
-noPinCutSpace     # Specifies name of the pin, wildcard can be specified
                   # (bool, optional)
-noViaCutSpace     #   (bool, optional)